  Answer Exit # Суки!

Speech 22 # Да, да, конечно! Наш чемпион. С удовольствием в...
  Answer Exit # О да!!!
    Demand Property Player DenBillRacingWin == 5
    Result Item Player powered_armor += 1
    Result Item Player blue_condom += 1
    Result Item Player rot_gut += 1
    Result Property Player DenBillRacingWin = 7

Speech 23 # Ага, почетное второе место. Получите вашу награ...
  Answer Exit # Ага, непременно. Если не подохну...
    Demand Property Player DenBillRacingWin == 4
    Result Property Player Experience += 5000
    Result Item Player magic_8_ball += 1
    Result Item Player nuka_cola += 30
    Result Property Player DenBillRacingWin = 6

Speech 24 # Запись окончена, извините. Приходите в следующи...
